race.comment: JOANJETT (10) is knocking on the door and is desperate to break through soon. Peak fitness now and doesn't have to improve much to get off the mark. INTELLIGENCER (9) has hit the line nicely in her two runs back and should be hitting her straps now. Drawn to blend into the race nicely when they straighten. Can give this a big shake. MISS WILDCAT (11) is a Jungle Cat filly on debut for the Wilson stable. Has shown positive signs in her lead-up work, readied with a recent Gold Coast trial. Drawn sticky but can play a role with a touch of luck. NINE MILL (5) is a Lonhro gelding on debut for Toby Edmonds. Readied with some soft trials and gets a key booking in Mallyon. Don't take lightly.
